item.title: Not all COVID-19 tests are created equal
item.author: Author
item.description: I hadn’t done much digging into the different COVID-19 tests availale until recently, when I had to take one in order to visit my boyfriend in Denmark under the country’s newly revised, surprisingly compassionate travel ban.
